Mach.f_contract_seed_cost(r_vals)¶
Dict

Contract seeding cost in each cashflow period, currently, contract cost is the same for all lmus and crops.

Mach.f_contractseeding_occurs()¶

This function just sets the period when contract seeding must occur (period when wet seeding begins). Contract seeding is not hooked up to yield penalty because if your going to hire someone you will hire them at the optimum time. Contract seeding is hooked up to poc so this param stops the model having late seeding.

Dict for pyomo.

Mach.f_harv_rate_period()¶
Dict for pyomo

Harv rate in each mach period for each crops. - account for crops that can be harvested early ie crops that can’t be harvested early are given 0 harv rate in the first harv period

Dict for pyomo

Calcs the penalty in each mach period (dry seeding and wet) - kg/ha/period/crop. Used in pyomo to calculate loss of cashflow and reduction in stubble
